    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Model Risk Level 2. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within acceptable error bounds across the full COU operating envelope. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied for all five evaluated flow-speed combinations (maximum RH = 0.87). The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device under the Minimal profile conformance level.",
